---
title: Carb Smart Fiesta Beyond Meat® Salad with Charred Corn Salsa and Chipotle Crema
description: Sweet, spicy and tangy flavours are on the menu tonight! Pork is sautéed in a smoky Tex-Mex seasoning, then paired with fresh spring mix salad topped with grilled corn and tomato salsa. A zingy chipotle crema brings a touch of freshness!
